- added support for simple and fast auth method using user's DN and password
- additional options in /etc/ldap.conf [example]:
   userconnect_check yes                    (to enable support)
   userdn cn=A_USER,ou=unit,o=org           (A_USER macro expanded to username)
- special thx to Michal Strzelczyk - for code, pepsi and fajki R1 :)
